istik und der Fachdidaktik werden die Chancen und Grenzen der europäischen Studienreform dargestellt und die inhaltlichen wie strukturellen Eckpunkte eines Kerncurriculums für den Bachelor-Studiengang Germanistik skizziert.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 4aBildung. 4aBildungsforschung. 4aBildungspolitik. 4aBologna-Prozess. 4aKerncurriculum. 4aLiteratur. 4aLiteraturwissenschaft. 4aStudiengangsreform. 4aUniversität. 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / European / German.2bisacsh  aEducation.  aEducational Policy.  aEducational Research.  aLiterary Studies.  aLiterature.  aUniversity.1 aBogdal, Klaus-Michael, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMein, Georg, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMein, Georg, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aParr, Rolf, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aRoggausch, Werner, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSchiewer, Hans-Jochen, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aWeingarten, Rüdiger, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Highlight Collection Complete Package 2000-2009z9783110463415oZDB-23-TSO08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Highlight Collection Lit. & Kultur 2000-2009z978311046340840uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783839405871zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839405871423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783839405871/original  a978-3-11-046340-8  transcript Highlight Collection Lit. & Kultur 2000-2009c2000d2009  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_LT  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-al